OL,3,CGovernment prepares for release of
OL,4,Clandmark review into ailing water
OL,5,Csector
OL,7,FThe Government is bracing for the
OL,8,Frelease of a landmark review into the
OL,9,Fwater industry, which could reportedly
OL,10,Flead to the abolition of embattled
OL,11,Fwater regulator Ofwat.
OL,13,FThe Independent Water Commission, led
OL,14,Fby former Bank of England deputy
OL,15,Fgovernor Sir Jon Cunliffe, will
OL,16,Foutline recommendations to turn around
OL,17,Fthe floundering sector in its final
OL,18,Freport on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
