OL,7,FThe review reportedly includes
OL,8,Fproposals to establish a new system of
OL,9,Fregulation, which is currently split
OL,10,Fbetween Ofwat, the Environment Agency
OL,11,Fand the Drinking Water Inspectorate.
OL,13,FMinisters will announce a consultation
OL,14,Fthat could lead to axing Ofwat, which
OL,15,Foversees how much water companies in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales can charge for
OL,17,Fservices, according to the Guardian.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
