OL,7,FOfwat has faced intense criticism for
OL,8,Foverseeing water companies during the
OL,9,Fyears that they paid shareholders and
OL,10,Faccrued large debts while ageing
OL,11,Finfrastructure crumbled and sewage
OL,12,Fspills skyrocketed.
OL,14,FIn an interview with the Sunday Times,
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed
OL,16,Fsuggested he was in favour of a new
OL,17,Fmodel where regional boards managed
OL,18,Fwater in their areas, including
OL,19,Frepresentatives from water companies,
OL,20,Flocal authorities and other
OL,21,Forganisations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
