OL,7,FHe said: "I think the catchment-based
OL,8,Fmodel has a lot to commend it. Because
OL,9,Fif you can manage what's going into
OL,10,Fthe water better, you can clean up the
OL,11,Fwater faster."
OL,13,FAsked on Friday if there were plans to
OL,14,Fscrap Ofwat as the regulator, Downing
OL,15,FStreet said the Government will wait
OL,16,Ffor a final report.
