OL,7,FA No 10 spokesman said: "We are
OL,8,Fwaiting for Sir Jon Cunliffe's final
OL,9,Freport next week, you can expect us to
OL,10,Fset out our response after that on
OL,11,Fwhat more we will do to turn the
OL,12,Fsector around."
OL,14,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,15,Fare not going to comment on
OL,16,Fspeculation." Ofwat declined to
OL,17,Fcomment.
