OL,7,FMr Reed is also expected to announce a
OL,8,Fnew Government pledge to halve sewage
OL,9,Fpollution from water companies by the
OL,10,Fend of the decade, during broadcast
OL,11,Finterviews on Sunday.
OL,13,FHe said: "Families have watched their
OL,14,Flocal rivers, coastlines and lakes
OL,15,Fsuffer from record levels of pollution.
OL,17,F"My pledge to you: the Government will
OL,18,Fhalve sewage pollution from water
OL,19,Fcompanies by the end of the decade."
