OL,7,FBut in his Sunday Times interview, he
OL,8,Facknowledged that bills were unlikely
OL,9,Fto fall from their current level,
OL,10,Fsaying instead that an investment of
OL,11,F#104 billion in the sector would
OL,12,F"avoid the need for any big bill hikes
OL,13,Fin the future".
OL,15,FIt comes after the Environment Agency
OL,16,Fon Friday said the number of serious
OL,17,Fpollution incidents caused by water
OL,18,Fcompanies across England rose by 60%
OL,19,Fin 2024 compared with the previous
OL,20,Fyear.
