OL,7,FThe figures showed companies recorded
OL,8,Fa total of 2,801 pollution incidents,
OL,9,Fup from 2,174 in 2023.
OL,11,FOf these, 75 were categorised as
OL,12,Fposing "serious or persistent" harm to
OL,13,Fwildlife and human health ` up from 47
OL,14,Flast year.
