OL,7,FThe Environment Agency said it is
OL,8,Fclear some companies are failing to
OL,9,Fmeet the targets it has set on
OL,10,Fpollution, attributing failures to
OL,11,Fpersistent underinvestment in new
OL,12,Finfrastructure, poor asset maintenance
OL,13,Fand reduced resilience because of the
OL,14,Fimpacts of climate change.
OL,16,FEarlier on Friday, the Public Accounts
OL,17,FCommittee also released a report which
OL,18,Fcalled the level of pollution "woeful"
OL,19,Fand recommended an overhaul of the
OL,20,Fregulation system.
