OL,7,FThe cross-party group of MPs said the
OL,8,FGovernment must act with urgency to
OL,9,Fstrengthen oversight of the sector to
OL,10,Frebuild trust and ensure its poor
OL,11,Fperformance improves.
OL,13,FThe Independent Water Commission
OL,14,Fpublished its interim report in June,
OL,15,Fwhich found the sector to be beset
OL,16,Fwith "deep-rooted, systemic" failures.
