OL,7,FWhile the paper outlined the
OL,8,Fcommission's direction of travel, it
OL,9,Fstopped short of providing detailed
OL,10,Frecommendations on policy, regulatory
OL,11,Freform and corporate governance, which
OL,12,Fare now expected in the final report.
OL,14,FThe interim review pointed to the need
OL,15,Ffor better regulation of water
OL,16,Fcompanies but it did not recommend the
OL,17,Fwholesale scrapping of Ofwat, which
OL,18,Fsome have urged.
