OL,7,FShadow environment secretary Victoria
OL,8,FAtkins said the Government should be
OL,9,F"transparent" about where the money to
OL,10,Ffix Britain's sewers was coming from,
OL,11,Fwarning that consumers may have to
OL,12,Fstump up some of the cash.
OL,14,FShe added: "Labour's water plans must
OL,15,Falso include credible proposals to
OL,16,Fimprove the water system's resilience
OL,17,Fto droughts, without placing an
OL,18,Fadditional burden on bill payers and
OL,19,Ftaxpayers."
